WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.280
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.280 --> 00:00:03.740
I have another video for you all today.

00:00:04.640 --> 00:00:10.160
The word that a lot of you all are getting at church is very lukewarm.

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:17.760
They're not teaching you how to stand on your faith, how to believe by faith, or how to pray in the Holy Ghost.

00:00:17.760 --> 00:00:24.080
You would not believe the emails and the questions about the Holy Spirit—that nobody knows how to pray in tongues.

00:00:24.080 --> 00:00:34.506
Nobody knows how to flow with the gifts and do what we are commissioned to do to be able to bring in the fire and get people free.

00:00:34.506 --> 00:00:38.640
A lot of people are so bound because of lack of knowledge.

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:42.980
It says in the Bible, "My people perish for a lack of knowledge.

00:00:43.320 --> 00:01:08.373
" I feel like God has commissioned me and put me on this platform to tell you what the Holy Spirit has told me and all the knowledge that I've received over the years from some big ministries just dumping into me, continually feeding on the Word and staying on that potter's wheel, allowing the Holy Spirit to mold me.

00:01:08.756 --> 00:01:15.484
In that process, the potter's wheel has equipped me to be able to come on here today and be able to help you all.

00:01:15.484 --> 00:01:26.820
The Lord gave me a Ferrari to drive—this beautiful Ferrari because I love Ferraris and I think they're really amazing cars.

00:01:26.820 --> 00:01:29.109
So He gave me this amazing Ferrari.

00:01:29.109 --> 00:01:34.000
This is the way the Lord showed me in the spirit whenever I pray over it.

00:01:34.423 --> 00:01:38.880
I'm borrowing this Ferrari and driving it everywhere.

00:01:39.360 --> 00:01:45.189
I'm so excited to have this Ferrari, but Dad—my Father—let me borrow it.

00:01:45.990 --> 00:01:51.566
I don't have the title deed to the Ferrari by myself; they're not my keys.

00:01:51.566 --> 00:01:57.140
It's not anything; He's just allowing me to drive it, kind of like I would allow my son to drive my car.

00:01:57.140 --> 00:02:00.879
It's not his, but I'm allowing him to use it.

00:02:00.879 --> 00:02:03.492
So, I'm not in control of the Ferrari.

00:02:04.445 --> 00:02:09.817
I'm just allowed to drive it every once in a while when God says, "Hey, here's the keys.

00:02:09.817 --> 00:02:10.686
Drive it.

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:19.440
" Everybody's so excited and thinks you're so cool because of that Ferrari, but the Ferrari was never yours to begin with.

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:23.280
And that's the way I look at the prophetic gifting.

00:02:23.280 --> 00:02:31.440
We have this treasure in earthen vessels that the excellency of the power will be known of Him and not of me.

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:33.786
I don't control any of it.

00:02:33.786 --> 00:02:35.919
I can't make it happen.

00:02:35.919 --> 00:02:41.280
If I could, I would operate in it all the time.

00:02:41.280 --> 00:02:43.378
It comes by dying.

00:02:43.378 --> 00:02:46.470
You have to die to self.

00:02:49.290 --> 00:02:56.623
He entrusts you with more, and the more He entrusts you with, you're faithful with that amount of anointing.

00:02:56.623 --> 00:03:01.863
You're faithful with that part of the prophetic gift and He'll make you ruler over much.

00:03:01.863 --> 00:03:09.819
But if you're not faithful with the little and you don't handle this, He wants to see if it's going to destroy you.

00:03:09.819 --> 00:03:17.560
This is what He's wanting to see: Can your character handle this gift?

00:03:17.560 --> 00:03:27.136
If it can't, He doesn't say, "I'm done with you and I'm not going to use you anymore," because the gifts and the callings of God are without repentance.

00:03:27.136 --> 00:03:28.423
They're on you regardless.

00:03:28.423 --> 00:03:36.583
But He wants to see if your character can handle that pressure of that gift, that Ferrari.

00:03:36.583 --> 00:03:45.760
Does the Ferrari change you, or do you just drive it and enjoy it until He says, "I need my keys back"?

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:48.844
It's the same way.

00:03:50.017 --> 00:03:54.008
If you can't handle it, this is what He does: He puts you back on the potter's wheel.

00:03:54.008 --> 00:03:57.748
He puts you back on the potter's wheel and that water starts spinning around and around.

00:03:59.120 --> 00:03:59.908
You go faster and faster.

00:04:00.434 --> 00:04:05.229
He dumps some more water on you and puts a little bit more pressure there.

00:04:05.229 --> 00:04:15.599
I have a man who emails me—I don't remember your name, sir, I'd have to ask my wife, she tells me the emails—but he's a master potter and he makes sculptures and pottery for people.

00:04:19.931 --> 00:04:22.212
He's brilliant; I've seen him do his work.

00:04:22.506 --> 00:04:31.085
As he does his work, he puts his finger and his pressure on that pot and it makes it into a beautiful vase.

00:04:31.508 --> 00:04:35.600
That's the way we are in the spirit realm, y'all.

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:40.020
If we're not ready, the Lord just puts us back on the potter's wheel.

00:04:40.020 --> 00:04:42.959
And this is the way it is a lot of times.

00:04:42.959 --> 00:04:55.010
I believe when you see people in the Bible, Moses took 80 years on the potter's wheel before he was used by God to go and lead the people out of Egypt.

00:04:55.010 --> 00:05:00.032
It took 80 years for him to be on that potter's wheel for him to be ready.

00:05:00.032 --> 00:05:10.126
It took 80 years for him to die to self: 40 years in the wilderness and 40 years being Pharaoh's son—80 altogether.

00:05:13.886 --> 00:05:14.251
And then God said, "You're ready.

00:05:14.251 --> 00:05:15.349
" He had a burning bush experience.

00:05:15.349 --> 00:05:18.419
In that experience of 80 years, most people would have said, "Man, I'm 80 years old.

00:05:18.419 --> 00:05:19.199
My life's over.

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:20.939
There's nothing that God can do with me.

00:05:20.939 --> 00:05:38.240
" If you're 80 years old and you feel a tug on your heart to do something—maybe it's to make videos, maybe it's to do a YouTube channel, maybe God's called you to do something big—it is not over until it's over, as long as you stay on that potter's wheel.

00:05:38.240 --> 00:05:48.629
I feel the Holy Ghost, and when it comes on me, I start crying.

00:05:48.639 --> 00:06:10.549
As long as you stay on that potter's wheel, God's going to keep using you until the day He calls you home; there's nothing too big for God to work out in your flesh because the steps of the righteous are ordered of the Lord.

00:06:13.111 --> 00:06:23.820
What I'm trying to tell you is it took Paul and some of the disciples three years walking with Jesus before they started walking fully in their giftings and their call.

00:06:23.820 --> 00:06:37.360
But if you start saying, "I have this treasure in an earthen vessel that the excellency of the power may be known of Him and not of me," He uses me; I don't use Him.

00:06:40.272 --> 00:06:42.773
Less of me, more of Him.

00:06:45.726 --> 00:06:54.960
In that process of being refined—the refiner's fire—what I'm trying to tell you all is what's coming to the body of Christ.

00:06:54.960 --> 00:06:59.931
There is a great revival that's about to take place—a massive outpouring.

00:06:59.931 --> 00:07:06.410
But I have told you what the Lord has showed me about a refiner's fire coming to His body.

00:07:06.410 --> 00:07:09.830
It is a massive move coming.

00:07:09.830 --> 00:07:12.228
Yes, it will be painful.

00:07:12.228 --> 00:07:16.205
A refiner's process is painful sometimes to the flesh.

00:07:16.205 --> 00:07:24.720
But in the process of the refiner's fire, it makes us less of us and more of Him.

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:32.756
We have a treasure in an earthen vessel that the excellency of the power will be known of Him and not of us.

00:07:32.756 --> 00:07:40.879
Whenever we are dying to self—dying to our emotions—most people say, "Well, I've paid the price.

00:07:40.879 --> 00:07:47.430
I moved my family to wherever to go to Bible school.

00:07:47.430 --> 00:07:48.000
" No.

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:54.820
A person who's selling insurance will relocate and be a part of a new state or a new town.

00:07:54.820 --> 00:07:59.851
People are moving from California to go live by Elon Musk in his new factory.

00:07:59.851 --> 00:08:04.260
They're not going through a refiner's process because you moved your family.

00:08:04.260 --> 00:08:07.280
A refiner's process is to die to self.

00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:11.128
It's not my will, but Yours be done.

00:08:11.128 --> 00:08:19.189
When you get in that dying to self—not my will, but Yours be done every single day—that's what does it.

00:08:19.189 --> 00:08:25.083
The Apostle Paul says, "I die daily to myself that Christ may live in me.

00:08:25.083 --> 00:08:26.897
" Christ needs to live in you.

00:08:26.897 --> 00:08:29.1000
You need to be at that spout where the glory comes out.

00:08:29.1000 --> 00:08:36.279
You need to be that person who is a yielded vessel that Jesus can use.

00:08:36.279 --> 00:08:54.711
Without being yielded and being dead to self, you'll never be that person that God can flow through to the point where blind eyes will open and deaf ears will pop open, the lame, the leper, the dead—all of it.

00:09:00.107 --> 00:09:11.786
Look at the process of even Jesus, the Son of God: 33 years before He even died for us.

00:09:11.786 --> 00:09:15.725
But He was 30 years old before He even started His ministry.

00:09:17.920 --> 00:09:34.900
Jesus had to go through a refiner's potter's process, anointed to the full, had the Holy Spirit without measure, and went through a process of 30 years before He even said to Mary, "It's not my time.

00:09:34.900 --> 00:09:40.240
" He even went through a process whenever He was turning the water into wine, His first miracle.

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:48.550
Look at everything He went through; we don't have an account in the Gospels really of everything that He went through for those 30 years.

00:09:48.550 --> 00:10:02.180
But you know, it was something that he was in me, memorizing the Bible verses, the Torah, things like that, getting the word down inside of him.

00:10:02.640 --> 00:10:04.686
There was a process.

00:10:04.686 --> 00:10:08.760
That's what I'm trying to tell you all: we die daily.

00:10:08.760 --> 00:10:19.800
And that's why I was trying to tell this young man on Facebook that I have no ability on my own.

00:10:21.600 --> 00:10:29.839
I am nothing without the Holy Spirit telling me what to tell you all on this camera.

00:10:29.839 --> 00:10:42.408
I am so desperate as a man with hardly any education, with hardly anything to lean on in the natural for my flesh; he has stripped everything away from me.

00:10:42.408 --> 00:10:47.698
I feel like a skeleton a lot of times with the wind blowing.

00:10:48.320 --> 00:10:51.219
I'm so thirsty.

00:10:51.219 --> 00:10:52.959
I'm so hungry.

00:10:52.959 --> 00:11:07.200
And I have to sit at his feet for everything in my life: finances, stuff going on in my own flesh, my family, my children, my little girl who is overcoming.

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:16.022
He keeps me in a place of desperation on him, stripping back all the flesh.

00:11:16.022 --> 00:11:39.600
Over the years, I've learned so much to lean on him, to seek him and I'll find him instead of trying to perform because of something I feel I have the ability to drive that Ferrari, and waiting on the Lord and being desperate in these end times.

00:11:39.600 --> 00:11:44.200
In the process of being desperate, I'll tell you a story.

00:11:44.727 --> 00:11:50.045
I put it on my Facebook trying to help people to tug them along the way.

00:11:50.045 --> 00:11:54.010
William Seymour in the Azusa Street Revival—he was blind in one eye.

00:11:54.010 --> 00:11:55.840
He was an African-American man.

00:11:55.840 --> 00:11:58.360
Prejudice was crazy back then.

00:11:58.360 --> 00:12:04.693
People were absolutely crazy over racial stuff, and he pressed through.

00:12:04.693 --> 00:12:07.039
He pressed through the refiner's fire.

00:12:07.039 --> 00:12:11.886
He pressed through the racial tension and all the stupidness of that.

00:12:33.646 --> 00:12:54.987
He pressed through it and refused to let the color of his skin, refused to let all the pressure from all of the drama from one eye or anything stop him from allowing himself to be used by God.

00:12:58.072 --> 00:12:58.448
It was a process.

00:12:58.448 --> 00:12:59.909
Here he was.

00:12:59.909 --> 00:13:05.370
Even whenever he started Azusa Street, he went in and started this in an old building.

00:13:05.370 --> 00:13:18.753
He would come down the stairs and put a box over his head and he would pray in that box until God would allow him to take it off and the glory would come in.

00:13:18.753 --> 00:13:27.999
This happened every single day for three and a half years, about the same time that Jesus was in his ministry.

00:13:27.999 --> 00:13:45.662
He walked in, and the power and the glory were so strong on him that his wife would have to sleep on the couch because the electricity, the power, and the Shekinah glory were so strong and manifested on him that it would even affect her sleep at night.

00:13:45.662 --> 00:13:48.196
If you touched him, the glory would flow out of him.

00:13:48.196 --> 00:13:51.396
But that came with a price, which is what I'm trying to tell you.

00:13:52.446 --> 00:13:54.137
It was a dying to self.

00:13:54.137 --> 00:14:00.320
Just like I'm trying to tell you what happens to me; it's a dying to self.

00:14:00.320 --> 00:14:10.735
Having a child with special needs, and the Lord tells you, 'Go and I want you to pray for people that are sick and I want you to lay hands on them.

00:14:10.735 --> 00:14:16.299
' And I say, 'Lord, I feel like a hypocrite.

00:14:16.299 --> 00:14:17.928
' 'Do it anyway.

00:14:17.928 --> 00:14:22.260
' And being obedient, God uses me and he touches people and they're healed.

00:14:22.260 --> 00:14:23.299
It's not me.

00:14:23.299 --> 00:14:30.746
If I could turn on that switch for myself, y'all, I would be able to pray for my little girl and see an instantaneous manifestation.

00:14:30.746 --> 00:14:37.679
I would go into these hospitals and pray for people and see them healed all the time.

00:14:38.839 --> 00:14:41.640
But the Lord turns the switch on, is what I'm trying to tell you.

00:14:41.640 --> 00:14:53.599
In the same way with William Seymour, he would sit there with that box on his head until the glory would settle in those meetings.

00:15:01.900 --> 00:15:02.160
And he would do that every single service.

00:15:02.160 --> 00:15:08.880
Sometimes it was five minutes, they say, and sometimes it was several hours, but he would just sit in there and they would sing songs.

00:15:08.880 --> 00:15:12.057
As crazy as that may sound, it's a humbling process.

00:15:12.057 --> 00:15:16.739
It's the Lord showing you: 'This is not your Ferrari.

00:15:16.739 --> 00:15:18.440
You're just borrowing it.

00:15:18.440 --> 00:15:24.373
' And when you get a hold of that, God will start using you.

00:15:24.373 --> 00:15:25.440
It's not about you.

00:15:25.440 --> 00:15:41.947
Yes, you can walk around with the zeal of a teenager and be excited that God has a call on your life, and it's like he tips his hat to you.

00:15:41.947 --> 00:15:45.600
But he says, 'Get on the wheel.

00:15:45.600 --> 00:15:52.856
Get on the wheel and then I'll use you and I'll do something big in your life.

00:15:52.856 --> 00:16:00.000
' Without the potter's wheel and dying to self, self is in the way.

00:16:00.000 --> 00:16:02.469
Flesh is in the way.

00:16:17.400 --> 00:16:17.760
And you've got to get self and flesh out of the way.

00:16:20.537 --> 00:16:31.257
And the way you get it on there is by getting on your knees, praying in the spirit, refiner's fire, getting in the word, continually dying daily to self.

00:16:38.600 --> 00:16:45.017
And in that process, it would be all of him and none of you.

00:16:45.017 --> 00:16:58.288
I have this treasure in an earthen vessel, that the excellency of the power will be known of you, Lord, and not of me.

00:17:09.965 --> 00:17:18.549
I hope this message helped you today.

00:17:18.559 --> 00:17:23.576
This is what I had on my heart.

00:17:23.576 --> 00:17:29.074
Let me pray for you right now.

00:17:29.074 --> 00:17:34.983
Let me agree with you in prayer for some things you're believing for.

00:17:37.440 --> 00:17:46.880
Father, right now in the name of Jesus, we come before you boldly and we thank you, Father, that my brothers and sisters are hungry for you.

00:17:46.880 --> 00:17:51.982
There's a great revival that's about to take place upon this country.

00:17:51.982 --> 00:17:55.075
You've showed me this great revival even today.

00:17:58.098 --> 00:17:58.400
You told me about the tents.

00:18:06.740 --> 00:18:07.070
You told me about the people.

00:18:07.070 --> 00:18:17.608
You told me about the manifestations and the glory of God coming in a wave like we've never seen before.

00:18:17.608 --> 00:18:20.500
But I thank you, Father, for the refiner's fire.

00:18:20.500 --> 00:18:22.091
Make me better.

00:18:22.091 --> 00:18:23.919
Make me pure.

00:18:23.919 --> 00:18:32.160
By the fire that does refine where the breath of God is sweeter, there his brightest glory shines.

00:18:32.160 --> 00:18:37.493
Lift us high up to the mountain into fellowship with you.

00:18:38.773 --> 00:18:43.840
And in that light, I'll see the fountain of his blood that cleanses you.

00:18:43.840 --> 00:18:48.960
Father, I thank you for the refining fire today.

00:18:48.960 --> 00:18:50.920
Touch these people, Father.

00:18:50.920 --> 00:18:57.120
Make them the vessel that can be used by you, Holy Spirit.

00:18:57.120 --> 00:19:06.903
Create in them a clean heart, Father, that we are more like you and less of us every single day.

00:19:12.280 --> 00:19:14.426
Father, we are not a branch that's separated from the vine, but we are a part of the vine.

00:19:17.039 --> 00:19:20.080
We are stuck to you; we are stuck onto the main part of the vine.

00:19:28.800 --> 00:19:29.440
And I thank you, Lord, that that's where the healing rivers flow.

00:19:29.440 --> 00:19:42.240
When you abide in me and my words abide in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.

00:19:42.240 --> 00:19:56.816
I call healing over their bodies right now in the name of Jesus, from the top of their heads to the soles of their feet.

00:19:56.816 --> 00:20:05.234
We decree and declare the healing power of God to flow on the inside of them right now.

00:20:05.234 --> 00:20:07.910
We take authority over sickness and disease.

00:20:07.910 --> 00:20:11.371
We take authority over diabetes.

00:20:11.371 --> 00:20:14.832
We take authority over heart disease.

00:20:14.832 --> 00:20:19.360
We take authority over liver cancers and fatty livers.

00:20:19.360 --> 00:20:26.377
We take authority over brain tumors and over all kinds of brain disorders, Alzheimer's, and dementia.

00:20:26.377 --> 00:20:32.639
We plead the blood of Jesus over the sickness right now.

00:20:32.639 --> 00:20:37.474
We take authority over all sickness and disease, whatever ails them in their body.

00:20:37.474 --> 00:20:52.840
We want to be at the spout where the glory comes out, Lord, in these last days, so that we are able to be used by you.

00:20:52.840 --> 00:21:14.205
Father, that we're able to be that vessel that is dead to self and you are alive in us—it's not us.

00:21:33.760 --> 00:21:39.319
We're not using you; you're using us, Father.

00:21:39.319 --> 00:21:43.013
It's not our gift; it's your gift and your ability in us.

00:22:03.829 --> 00:22:04.354
Oh Lord, I praise you God for the Holy Spirit.

00:22:04.354 --> 00:22:10.308
He is the comforter and he dwells on the inside of us.

00:22:10.308 --> 00:22:13.080
Help us to go higher.

00:22:13.080 --> 00:22:16.880
Help us to soar on wings like eagles.

00:22:16.880 --> 00:22:23.069
Help us to be more like you.

00:22:23.069 --> 00:22:28.337
Less of us and more of you.

00:22:31.665 --> 00:22:39.337
For in that, Father, is where the glory lies for this last outpouring that you want to do upon this earth.

00:22:39.337 --> 00:22:45.383
Father, I thank you, Lord, that you create in us a clean heart.

00:22:45.383 --> 00:22:57.434
Create in me a clean heart, Lord, for the eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth looking for a heart that is perfect towards him.

00:22:57.434 --> 00:23:01.211
Father, let your eyes rest upon me today.

00:23:01.211 --> 00:23:10.613
Let your eyes rest, Lord, so that you're not having to look throughout the whole earth anymore.

00:23:10.613 --> 00:23:20.110
Let us be that vessel that you're looking for for this end-time outpouring to save the lost.

00:23:20.110 --> 00:23:22.310
Create in us a clean heart, Lord.

00:23:30.053 --> 00:23:31.653
Father, I thank you for the end-time outpouring, for creative miracles; blinded eyes will see, deaf ears will hear, and the dead will rise again.

00:23:31.653 --> 00:23:35.999
Greater works will we do, Lord, as you said.

00:23:35.999 --> 00:23:37.920
Help us to be the salt.

00:23:37.920 --> 00:23:43.538
Help us to be that salt that makes people thirsty.

00:23:46.213 --> 00:23:47.440
When we go into places, Father, let us not be preaching to them without fire.

00:23:47.440 --> 00:24:04.192
Father, let the glory of God be so manifest and made manifest on us that when we go into those places, the glory of God would shine upon our faces like it did for Moses when he had his burning bush experience.

00:24:04.192 --> 00:24:21.600
He did that under the old covenant, Lord, and we have a new covenant.

00:24:21.600 --> 00:24:46.240
Come visit us once again, oh God; come visit us once again.

00:24:46.240 --> 00:25:40.480
Give us a burning bush experience, Father, so that the glory would shine upon our faces, that people would see the light and the glory on our lives.

00:26:37.279 --> 00:26:38.320
And all we can do is turn them to you and tell them about how good God is and how much you love us and how much you did for us on that cross.

00:27:03.400 --> 00:27:24.507
Father, I give you glory and honor and praise for everybody that you're going to use; there is going to be a major outpouring of your spirit on these people.

00:27:24.507 --> 00:27:49.072
The people on this YouTube channel who are watching me right now are here for such a time as this.

00:27:49.072 --> 00:28:13.543
It's about the last harvest of souls that you told me you desire so much.

00:28:25.679 --> 00:29:18.480
You said, "I wish that all men would come unto me," and as in John, "For God so loved the world that he gave his one and only begotten son that whosoever believes in him should not perish but have everlasting life.

00:29:33.269 --> 00:29:57.387
" I thank you, Father, that that's what you're wanting to do in these days—that you gave your love and you gave your life for us so that we would have a saving knowledge of Jesus Christ and a revelation of what you did when you said, "I give you a comforter, and the comforter is going to come and abide in you.

00:29:57.387 --> 00:30:08.799
" He's going to come and abide in you; he's going to come and set the captives free through you, and that's the great Holy Spirit.

